              </h2>
              <p class="text-white/60 text-sm mt-1">Ownership and rights</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="space-y-4 text-white/80">
            <p>
              The IEEE UC San Diego Student Branch name, logo, and all content and materials
              available through our Services, including text, graphics, website
              name, code, images, and logos, are the property of IEEE UC San Diego Student Branch or
              its licensors and are protected by applicable intellectual
              property laws.
            </p>
            <p>
              The IEEE name and logo are trademarks of the Institute of
              Electrical and Electronics Engineers, Inc. and are used with permission
              under license from IEEE.
            </p>
            <p>
              UC San Diego logos and trademarks are used with permission from the
              University of California, San Diego.
            </p>
            <p>
              Other company logos displayed on our platform are used solely to
              represent partnerships and sponsorships with those organizations.
            </p>
            <div class="bg-base-300/50 rounded-lg p-4 border border-white/5">
              <p class="text-sm">
                You are granted a limited, non-exclusive, non-transferable
                license to access and use our Services for personal,
                non-commercial purposes in accordance with these Terms.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- 6. User Content -->
        <div
          class="bg-base-200/80 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-2xl shadow-lg border border-white/10 p-8 hover:border-ieee-yellow/30 transition-colors"
          id="user-content"
        >
          <div class="flex items-start gap-4 mb-6">
            <div class="p-3 bg-ieee-yellow/10 rounded-xl">
              <svg
                class="w-6 h-6 text-ieee-yellow"
                fill="none"
                stroke="currentColor"
                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              >
                <path
                  stroke-linecap="round"
                  stroke-linejoin="round"
                  stroke-width="2"
                  d="M7 16a4 4 0 01-.88-7.903A5 5 0 1115.9 6L16 6a5 5 0 011 9.9M15 13l-3-3m0 0l-3 3m3-3v12"
                ></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white">6. User Content</h2>
              <p class="text-white/60 text-sm mt-1">
                Content you submit to our Services
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="space-y-4 text-white/80">
            <p>
              You may submit content to our Services, including profile
              information, resumes, receipts, and other materials ("User
              Content"). By submitting User Content, you:
            </p>
